snippet.title: This is SpyParty, old v2
snippet.description:
You can play SpyParty now or get more info at http://www.spyparty.com

The background music is A Buck and Some Change by Hank Hirsh, which is one of the excellent jazz songs available for including in your videos for free on YouTube.

The old art version of this trailer is here:  https://youtu.be/J5BAD4YrS34
